articles.author: Reuters
articles.title: USS Canberra: US commissions first Navy warship in foreign port - Reuters
articles.description: The United States commissioned a warship in Sydney, Australia, on Saturday, the first time a U.S. Navy vessel joined active service at a foreign port, as the two close allies step up their military ties in response to China's expanding regional reach.
